text.section:
The Department may adopt regulations to permit exceptions to this section, including exceptions for:
Economic hardship;
Vessels participating or preparing to participate in a U.S. Coast Guard or Department approved race or event;
The testing, repair, or development of vessel engines conducted by a bona fide engine or boat manufacturer or service person; and
Vessels belonging to a volunteer fire department, ambulance company, rescue squad company, or advance life support company or a political subdivision.
